      </p>
               
      <p>
      The <a href="http://www.railscamps.com">Rails Camps</a> usually attract 100-150 people twice a year, and <a href="http://rubyconf.org.au/2015">RubyConf AU</a> is around 500 people. Not everyone can make it to those events, though… so maybe there’s at least a thousand active Rubyists in Australia?
      </p>              
